                           <list>
                              <item>
                                 <p>Vellum, 9 1/2 in. by 6 5/8, consisting of 88 leaves, mostly in good preservation. The quires, 9 in number, are signed with letters from <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܓ</foreign> to <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܟܐ</foreign>. Each page is divided into two columns, of from 25 to 38 lines.</p>
